{
  "texts": [
    "AI is having a profound impact across a wide range of dental specialties, improving both clinical outcomes and patient care.",
    "Mohan et al.",
    "(22) assert that despite concerns regarding patient privacy and potential misinterpretations, the integration of AI-driven care systems in dentistry will improve patient care, encourage innovative research, and require collaboration across various professional fields in the future.",
    "However, the authors advocate for additional research, specifically randomized clinical trials, to solidify AI's efficacy in dental practice, aiming for data-driven, superior dental care that revolutionizes treatment delivery.",
    "Thilagar et al."
  ]
}